how to attract a stray cat i have a cat which is currently years old and i came home late last night and saw him playing with a stray cat i tried to approach him and the other cat but the other cat was scared and ran away what is the best way to get the stray to accept me and possibly let me get close to him her and would it be possible to use my cat as help since the stray isnt bothered by my cat leave some food out for it and maybe something with your scent on it if you see it stand at a distance for a little while to let it get used to you slowly approach it in a non threatening way if scares away back away and start over have some food with you to lure it to you it might take a while if it has been running wild for a while Cat Animal communication Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Dog Pittsburgh Steelers Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Leopard Kakapo Hedgehog Feral Cats (musical) Silent Night, Deadly Night Stray Cats American Black Bear Brown Bear Chicago Cubs Maison Ikkoku Lady and the Tramp Lion Feral cat Falconry Hersheypark Cheetah Domestication Fancy rat Taikyoku shogi The Amazing Maurice and his Educated Rodents Trailer Park Boys Tom and Jerry (MGM) Alley Cat Glossary of nautical terms Felidae Skunk Baseball Stars Albatross Pok__mon Live! Planet Waves Snooker Heinkel He 112 Dai shogi Ranma __ characters Asteroid Ferret Rent (musical) Carolina Panthers Amusement park USS Uhlmann (DD-687) Toronto Blue Jays SMTV Live The Cat Empire Brian Setzer Wrigley Field Through The Past, Darkly (Big Hits Vol. 2) Halloween National Football League Anarchist symbolism Pet skunk Johnny Appleseed Janeane Garofalo St. Louis Cardinals Milton H. Erickson Paulette Goddard Looney Tunes and Merrie Melodies filmography Animal rights Animal Liberation Front Druid (World of Warcraft) Hamster Nepeta Maka dai dai shogi Time travel Treecat The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe Scream (film) Giant Panda Tag Semiconductor device Software engineering Blink-182 Red Fox Ginny Weasle